{"tid":1234601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英超踢38場，頭兩場有失波就叫失敗？","createTime":"2019-06-17T03:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:41:25.000Z","uid":13754,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bda54d1f5eb749f58dcf66c637915a85841fa46","tid":1234601,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"我哋只係踢咗幾場互有得失嘅波，未去到4月都未知冠軍花落誰家<br />\n<br />\n如果而家只係因為有失波，有黃牌就覺得失敗<br />\n<br />\n咁你同考第二都會喊嘅林鄭有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家放棄行動一兩次就會有成果嘅期望，預備自己去打持久戰<br />\n<br />\n1. 鍛鍊身體，令自己更強壯，保護自己，保護我哋嘅兄弟姊妹<br />\n2. 學定急救，噚日遊行嘅急救人手真係好唔夠<br />\n3. 去睇敵人對付我哋嘅方法，我哋一齊去諗策略<br />\n<br />\n我哋只要堅持，我哋只會離成功愈嚟愈近，離失敗愈嚟愈遠，唔好忘記曼德拉坐咗咁耐監，佢冇放棄<br />\n<br />\n佢喺監獄日日健身做掌上壓，就係為咗迎接勝利嘅一日"},{"pid":"aa3e077532ea488af8e103a8e8bbb1ea5186555d","tid":1234601,"uid":13754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"鳩坐鳩叫失敗係小學雞行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70e27367e20d211ac2c0b39686e4411eb11e0c0","tid":1234601,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2117d4dd1ffb7065f7ee29c1fc472172d815f52c","tid":1234601,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"823111e6eebb30cb720e1317e8edcfd2206217a0","tid":1234601,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"要上熱門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0374d1cfd88ece5c5f017f0436cef270f3108415","tid":1234601,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"速龍 = 跣腳 = 謝拉特 = 利物浦 = 冇英超<br />\n利迷, 你地最清楚"},{"pid":"b26e744628edb9464aeeaccaedf380385386d8fd","tid":1234601,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0374d1cfd88ece5c5f017f0436cef270f3108415","tid":1234601,"uid":